data.description: The feel of the UP, right in mid-Michigan! Tucked away in the woods of this 15 acre parcel sits an incredible 3 bedroom 2 bathroom custom built log cabin style ranch. You are set up for off-grid living with solar panels with Generac battery backup, heat pump, prime hunting and stocked pond. The kitchen has been completely updated with gorgeous wood cabinets, custom countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Every bit of the wood exterior, deck and covered front porch have all been recently stained and a new metal roof was recently installed. Currently set up as a two bedroom with main floor laundry, but move the brand new ventless combined washer/dryer to the basement and you have the third bedroom back. Along with the detached 2.5 car garage, there is a 24x48 pole barn to store all your off road toys and hunting gear. A creek runs through the backwoods but it's accessible but a large steel frame bridge that can hold a semi! St. Johns Schools. Just minutes from US-127.
